      </item>
      <item>
        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To require the Federal Government to provide mental health services to each child who has been separated from one or more parent as a result of implementation of the Trump Administration's zero tolerance policy at the United States border, and for other purposes.</title>
